CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of woman wearing earrings and light colored strapless gown with bow on bodice, posed with man in front of light colored curtains in interior with patterned carpeting for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
